data.description: THIS HOME QUALIFIES FOR DOWN PAYMENT ASSISTANCE!  Up to $8000 in down payment available.  See attached for details!  Wow a 4 bedroom remodeled home with a one car garage in St. Petersburg!  Take a look at this beautiful home. When seller's purchased the home in 2020 the home had just been remodeled featuring new flooring, new A/C unit, new kitchen, new bathrooms, new stainless steel appliances, new water heater, and fresh coat of paint. Roof was put on in 2020 as well as a new water heater and new A/C - all in 2020.  The major items have been taken care of with this property. Four nice sized bedrooms with the washer/dryer hookups (stackable) inside the home (not the garage) like most.  Two full bathrooms that have been updated. This property has a garage with private access to the kitchen. There is a back entrance to the property through the alley in the east side of the lot, which is private and very convenient for a RV/Boat or just simply for an extra private parking entrance. The Master bedroom is conveniently located separately from the other rooms. You can also use the Master Bedroom as an in-law suite as it has its own outside entrance.  Front porch and back patio.  Large yard with plenty of room for all your toys, or to add a pool! Less than 3.5 miles from downtown St. Petersburg (a quick 10 minute drive) to enjoy all that St. Petersburg has to offer. Lake Maggiore Shore is Centrally located just minutes from vibrant Downtown St Pete with its shops, restaurants, museums, parks and entertainment and only 15 minutes from the Beautiful Gulf Beaches. This home is truly TURN KEY!!!  NO HOA and NO FLOOD ZONE - What are you waiting for? First come, first served.
